# jetbrains-app|version-globbed live product dir|product subdir|-
# Captures each IDE's product-specific remainder into config/jetbrains-settings/
# <Product>/ (version-normalised, outside the chezmoi seed tree, never deployed).
# The shared "feel the same" subset is maintained once in _shared/ via
# 'just jetbrains-promote' and written into the IDEs by 'just jetbrains-apply'.
# The first listed product is the canonical source for _shared/. See AGENTS.md.
jetbrains-app|.config/JetBrains/PhpStorm*|PhpStorm|-
jetbrains-app|.config/JetBrains/WebStorm*|WebStorm|-
jetbrains-app|.config/JetBrains/DataGrip*|DataGrip|-
jetbrains-app|.config/JetBrains/IntelliJIdea*|IntelliJIdea|-
jetbrains-app|.config/JetBrains/PyCharm*|PyCharm|-
